 the duration of the experiment -- the pendulum and foil were directly electrica
lly connected.
 While we cannot measure the contact potential, past experience suggests
 that it is 
\begin_inset Formula $\sim0.2-1$
\end_inset


\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

V.
 Minimizing the size of this potential is the single most effective change
 we could make to yield improved performance.
\end_layout

