\begin_layout Standard
A minor concern was the occasional 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

clock roll
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
 The timekeeping on the attractor and pendulum DAQ systems was referenced
 to the Windows clock, which reports time as a 32-bit integer number of
 milliseconds.
 If the DAQ program runs for more than 49 days without restarting, the 32-bit
 integer will overflow.
